==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊn|-əʊn]]

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''cone''' (''plural:'' '''[[cones]]''')
# {{geometry}} A [[surface of revolution]] formed by [[rotate|rotating]] a [[line]] around another line that intersects the first line.
# {{geometry}} A [[solid of revolution]] formed by rotating a [[triangle]] around a line through and in the plane of the triangle.
# Anything shaped like a cone.
# An [[ice-cream cone]].
# A unit of volume, applied solely to [[marijuana]] and only while it is in a [[smokable]] state; roughly 1.5 [[cubic centimetre]]s, depending on use.

====Synonyms====
*(''geometry''): [[conical surface]]
*(''ice-cream cone''): [[cornet]], [[ice-cream cone]]

